  <brief_title>Corticosteroid Dosage for Crohn's Disease Flare</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized Trial Comparing the Efficacy of Body-weight Based Versus Fixed Corticosteroid Dosage on Remission in Patients With Moderate to Severe Crohn's Disease Flares</official_title>
  <sponsors>
